description: 14 Diaries of the Great War War Documentary hosted by George Morris, published by Looks Film & TV in 2014 - English narration http://docuwiki.net/images/c/c3/14-Diaries-of-the-Great-War-Cover.jpg Information ------------------------------ 14 Diaries of the Great War retells the story of the greatest war mankind had ever seen in a unique way - it lets viewers experience World War I solely through the eyes of those who lived it. From over 1,000 very dramatic stories of the war, left behind in diaries, letters, postcards and telegrams, 14 of the most vivid and emotional have been chosen, deriving from characters all over the globe.
